(e) Funeral Parlors/Mortuaries;
(f)
Nightclubs/Cabarets/Places of Assembly/Membership Organizations;
(g) Repair shops;
(h) Eating Establishments/Restaurants:
(i) Retail Sales;
(j) Stables and kennels;
(k) Motor vehicle repair (major and minor) and paint shops.
